OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FKnown around the world, the Clifton
OL,8,FSuspension Bridge has stood proudly
OL,9,Fover Bristol for almost 160 years and,
OL,10,Funsurprisingly, like anything that
OL,11,Fold, it's starting to show its age.
OL,13,FSo from the middle of April, work will
OL,14,Fstart to give Brunel's landmark a
OL,15,Fmakeover.
