OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FNothing too radical from what you see
OL,8,Fnow, but after spending several
OL,9,Fmillion pounds over the next two
OL,10,Fyears, those responsible for the
OL,11,Fbridge's upkeep promise it will look
OL,12,Fbetter than ever.
OL,14,F"The paint is beginning to flake off.
OL,15,FThe coatings are getting a bit
OL,16,Fbrittle, so it's important we do
OL,17,Fthis," explains Trish Johnson, the
OL,18,Fstructure's first female Bridgemaster.
