OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,F"It gets done every 20 to 25 years and
OL,8,Fhas to be done by hand. There are
OL,9,Fspecially made tools to take off all
OL,10,Fthe loose paint and then to paint it
OL,11,Fall with three coats.
OL,13,F"It's going to be the same colour
OL,14,Fagain. It's a grade I listed structure
OL,15,Fafter all."
