OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FStraddling the borders of Bristol and
OL,8,FNorth Somerset, the private road has
OL,9,Fto pay its own way which means every
OL,10,Fpound to cross in each direction will
OL,11,Fbe used for this huge refurbishment
OL,12,Fjob.
OL,14,FUp to 10,000 daily journeys bring in
OL,15,Fup to #3 million annually but it'll
OL,16,Fcost more than that to pay for what is
OL,17,Fthe biggest undertaking since the
OL,18,Fbridge was finished in 1864.
