OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,FBecause it's not only a new paint job
OL,8,Fabout to begin but an undertaking to
OL,9,Fsee the bridge in a whole new light.
OL,11,F"There will be new LED lights to
OL,12,Fhighlight the chains," adds Trish,
OL,13,F"and we'll also have coloured lights
OL,14,Fas well so at some stage when there is
OL,15,Fan event on in Bristol we may be able
OL,16,Fto align ourselves with that.
OL,18,F"I think this is the first time we'll
OL,19,Fhave coloured lights on the bridge.
