OL,3,CMillions of pounds & two years' work:
OL,4,Cthe makeover of Clifton Suspension
OL,5,CBridge
OL,7,F"We're trying to highlight the
OL,8,Fstructure of the bridge, so it'll be
OL,9,Fmuch more about highlighting the
OL,10,Fchains, the deck and the towers. And
OL,11,Fit won't spill out so much into the
OL,12,FGorge below. So it should be tidier
OL,13,Fand look much better, I think.
OL,15,F"One thing's for sure, you'll still
OL,16,Fknow you're home when you see the
OL,17,Flights of the Clifton Suspension
OL,18,FBridge."
